column526: The Library was without a Director prior to the start of FY 15 through mid-August 2014 and then again from mid-November 2014 through the end of April 2015. The Director is also the Library\'s only full-time employee. In addition, the Town is still working to complete a renovation project to move the Library to its new location. The interim director (who is the part-time Assistant Director) was often focused on the project, in addition to her day-to-day duties. I\'ve only been here for a few months now, but I believe that these factors greatly impacted the services offered by the Library.
